{"tid":1960544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李慧琼：對9月能夠維持公平立法會選舉沒有信心！","createTime":"2020-04-06T08:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T12:22:16.000Z","uid":63113,"like":2,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"7b2bf20effe0024d34a3d226d3fc7bd7b20b9776","tid":1960544,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da94810e477e908f5331c1a4cac16391d146da2c","tid":1960544,"uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:26:26.000Z","msg":"民建聯主席李慧琼批評選管會就9月立法會選舉推出的選舉活動指引的建議離地，對能夠維持公平選舉沒有信心，擔心暴力一旦再出現，政府當局和選管會又再將責任交給警方，被問到9月立法會選舉有否需要押後，她認為，如果有因素影響選舉公平公正，政府就應該想辦法補救。<br />\n<br />\n李慧琼表示，在去年的區議會選舉，有民建聯候選人遇襲，辦事處多次遭受破壞，但選管會「隻眼開隻眼閉」，未有提出措施應對；而政府未有採用電子方式領票和點票，是非常落後，批評政府鴕鳥政策。民建聯支持優先讓長者投票的建議，但難以理解敬老的安排也要進行諮詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279031&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279031%26csid%3D261_341&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLYE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=13c2152d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279031&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"ce3756afcf688d1b3905d7d9ab277f5b87e71ab4","tid":1960544,"uid":41873,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:26:41.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n過去咁多屆邊有一屆係公平<br />\n屌你老母做雞俾狗屌"},{"pid":"784f38bad9e863ba23736bf0eb95d971474d601a","tid":1960544,"uid":169074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:28:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1bba95fb17c0e34daf78d6e334ff5b851b7f78b6","tid":1960544,"uid":63113,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:28:21.000Z","msg":"對自己選情不利=不公平選舉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8kdQpco.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8kdQpco.gif